OL,4,Chome residents company
OL,6,FDiane said: "They (the students) are
OL,7,Fso sure of themselves - in a nice way.
OL,8,FThey look at you as if to say, 'Are
OL,9,Fyou going to say? Or are you going to
OL,10,Fdo?' and it made you want to talk."
OL,11,FThe care home's activity and wellbeing
OL,12,Fmanager Sharon Wilczynski said the
OL,13,Fscheme had given the residents a "new
OL,14,Flease of life".
OL,16,F"They are talking about things which
OL,17,Fto the children are almost history but
OL,18,Ffor the residents it is their lives.
OL,19,FIt is what they lived," she said.J"So
OL,20,Fit is the two generations
OL,21,Finterlocking."
