OL,4,Chome residents company
OL,6,FSome students have started to visit
OL,7,Ftheir new friends in their spare time.
OL,8,FTeacher Megi Currie said they got as
OL,9,Fmuch out of it as the residents.JShe
OL,10,Fsaid: "They value the older
OL,11,Fgenerations. They value each other.
OL,12,FThey are really keen to come and do a
OL,13,Fgood thing. They saw that opportunity
OL,14,Fstraight away that this is a lovely
OL,15,Fthing to do and they just jumped at
OL,16,Fit.J"They are so personable. They
OL,17,Flisten. They care. They are just
OL,18,Feverything that you need, rolled into
OL,19,Fone. And we are proud of that."
